    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/035b33c43f69be06087580d91e89eba6.avif?t=1758925949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras_big/035b33c43f69be06087580d91e89eba6.avif?t=1758925949 width=800 height=108 /></span><i><strong></strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/afda0157e05e16da4ddbeb735b7b1f78.poster.avif?t=1758925949\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/afda0157e05e16da4ddbeb735b7b1f78.webm?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/afda0157e05e16da4ddbeb735b7b1f78.mp4?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a quirky adventure with four unique main characters as they seek their truth, battling gods, colossal corporations, and bizarre foes along the way. Unravel the Eternal Eclipse mystery and uncover the world's ancient secrets! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>This story contains adult humor and some mature themes. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/e5416413a33520407f4935d3ca48b686.avif?t=1758925949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras_big/e5416413a33520407f4935d3ca48b686.avif?t=1758925949 width=800 height=117 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Navigate the world with a platformer-inspired system, allowing you to climb, jump off, and hoist up ledges, breaking free from classic grid-based movement.</strong> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/3bb7a9021593d490fd326a44c9cb11e6.poster.avif?t=1758925949\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/3bb7a9021593d490fd326a44c9cb11e6.webm?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/3bb7a9021593d490fd326a44c9cb11e6.mp4?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/3868591533587a9f5676f603d7654d6d.avif?t=1758925949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras_big/3868591533587a9f5676f603d7654d6d.avif?t=1758925949 width=800 height=142 /></span>- <strong>Engage in combat with active player input during attack animations (timed hits), incorporating dodging and parrying. Special moves feature minigame sequences for extra damage.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/7869a445707aeba989bf623ccaca78dd.poster.avif?t=1758925949\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/7869a445707aeba989bf623ccaca78dd.webm?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/7869a445707aeba989bf623ccaca78dd.mp4?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/d6737f32aeae5765d411343e7cdf7138.avif?t=1758925949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras_big/d6737f32aeae5765d411343e7cdf7138.avif?t=1758925949 width=800 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Blending pixel art, with beautiful rendering, taking inspiration from ancient and modern Mexican culture and legends, but also having its own identity and personality.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/46db45027d988a4fc591b46687813dec.poster.avif?t=1758925949\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/46db45027d988a4fc591b46687813dec.webm?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/46db45027d988a4fc591b46687813dec.mp4?t=1758925949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras/1f8ab29ffabc46b63e5a4bbe888b208a.avif?t=1758925949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039920/extras_big/1f8ab29ffabc46b63e5a4bbe888b208a.avif?t=1758925949 width=800 height=23 /></span></p>",
